@host = http://localhost:4000
@scenarioVersion = {{$timestamp}}

### Cadastrar usuário "owner" para autenticar (201)
# @name registerOwner
POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin Owner",
  "email": "owner-banner-{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login para obter token (200)
# @name loginOwner
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner-banner-{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

###
@token = {{loginOwner.response.body.token}}

### Criar categoria para usar nos banners (201)
# @name createCategory
POST {{host}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Categoria Banner"
}

### Upload de imagem de banner (201, retorna { imageUrl } absoluta, sem precisar do banner já existir)
POST {{host}}/banners/upload-image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="banner.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./product-image-sample.png
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Criar banner 1 (201)
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner1.png",
  "position": 0,
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_CATEGORY_ID"
}

### Criar banner 2 (201)
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner2.png",
  "position": 1,
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_CATEGORY_ID"
}

### Criar banner 3 (201)
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner3.png",
  "position": 2,
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_CATEGORY_ID"
}

### Criar banner 4 (422, errors[] inclui banner.max_reached)
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner4.png",
  "position": 3,
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_CATEGORY_ID"
}

### Listagem ordenada por position (200)
GET {{host}}/banners?page=1&perPage=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar banner (204) — permitido mesmo com 3 banners existentes
# Substitua o id abaixo por um id de banner existente.
@bannerId = REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_BANNER_ID
PUT {{host}}/banners/{{bannerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner1-atualizado.png",
  "position": 0,
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_CATEGORY_ID"
}

### Criar banner com categoria inexistente (erro — FK inválida)
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner.png",
  "position": 0,
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000"
}

### Excluir banner existente (204)
DELETE {{host}}/banners/{{bannerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Excluir banner inexistente (404, errors[] inclui banner.not_found)
DELETE {{host}}/banners/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listagem pública da vitrine (200, sem JWT, ordenada por position)
GET {{host}}/storefront/banners

### Acesso sem JWT em /banners é bloqueado (401)
GET {{host}}/banners?page=1&perPage=20

### Criar banner com linkUrl como destino, sem categoryId (201)
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner-link.png",
  "position": 0,
  "linkUrl": "https://wa.me/5511999998888"
}

### Criar banner sem categoryId e sem linkUrl (422, errors[] inclui banner.destination.required)
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner-sem-destino.png",
  "position": 0
}

### Criar banner com categoryId e linkUrl juntos (422, errors[] inclui banner.destination.exclusive)
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner-dois-destinos.png",
  "position": 0,
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_CATEGORY_ID",
  "linkUrl": "https://wa.me/5511999998888"
}

### Criar banner com imageUrlMobile (201) — imagem específica para telas pequenas
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner-desktop.png",
  "imageUrlMobile": "https://cdn.example.com/banner-mobile.png",
  "position": 0,
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_CATEGORY_ID"
}

### Criar banner sem imageUrlMobile (201) — permanece null
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner-so-desktop.png",
  "position": 0,
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_CATEGORY_ID"
}

### Criar banner com imageUrlMobile inválida (422, errors[] inclui banner.imageUrlMobile.url)
POST {{host}}/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/banner.png",
  "imageUrlMobile": "not-a-url",
  "position": 0,
  "categoryId": "REPLACE_WITH_EXISTING_CATEGORY_ID"
}
